                    </div>
                </div>
                <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto 0;">                
                    <div style="font-size: 16px; color: #252525; margin: 15px 0; line-height: 20px;">
                        The following item(s) have been refunded:</p>
                        <table style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 10px;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th style="font-family: Raleway; line-height: 20px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;text-align: left; color: #252525; border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4; padding: 7px;">Description</th>
                                    <th style="font-family: Raleway; line-height: 20px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;text-align: left; color: #252525; border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4; padding: 7px;">Quantity</th>
